  answer: tajMahal
  hints:
  - The complex includes stunning reflection pools and well-maintained gardens.
  - Built using white marble and adorned with precious gemstones, this construction
    involved skilled artisans and craftsmen.
  - Commissioned by Emperor Shah Jahan in memory of his beloved wife Mumtaz Mahal.
  hintsPortuguese:
  - "O complexo inclui espelhos d'\xE1gua deslumbrantes e jardins bem cuidados."
  - "Constru\xEDda em m\xE1rmore branco e adornada com pedras preciosas, esta obra
    envolveu artes\xE3os e oper\xE1rios habilidosos."
  - "Encomendado pelo Imperador Shah Jahan em mem\xF3ria de sua amada esposa Mumtaz
    Mahal."
